      "text": "N tas Kehntisch Zede-\\tjus/ Zostjus Dehls\\waldija Zekantjus Wee-tá/ ta Dehla Jojakima/ ko Ne-bukadNezars tas Kehntisch no Babeles par Kehnizu bij eezeh-lis eeksch tahs Semmes Juhda."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet nedś wiꞥſch / nedś winna Kalpt/ nedś tee Landis tahs Semmes klausija teem Waherdeem ta KUNGĀ/ ko Wiꞥſch bij runnajs zaar Jere-miju to Praweetu."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr fuhttija tas Keh-ntisch Zedektjus Zukatu Setemi-jus Dehlu/ un Sewantju Mase-jus Dehlu to Preestert pee Jere-miju to Praweetu/ un likke faz-ziht: Luhds jelle preekſch nuums to KUNGĀ tawu Deewu."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo Jeremijus gabje wehl eekſcha un ahra starp teem Landim/ un tas wehl ne bija Zeetu-mā liks."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Warauſs Karra-Spehks bij zehlees no Egiptes. Sem-"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad notikke ta KUNGA Wahrdś uhs to Praweetu Jere-miju/ uu fazzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tā faſka tas KUNGS/ tas Isräēta Deewś: Tā buhs jums fazzibt us to Kehntzu no Juhda/ kas juhs pee mannim irr fuhttig manni waizaht : Raugi/ Warauſs Karra-Spehks / kas jutis par Paligu irr iegahjis/ greesifees atpakak us tawu Semmi/ us Egipti."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Kaldeēri nahks at-pakak / un karrohs prett tcho Pilssfahtu/ un uhsuems to / un fadedsinahs to ar Uggunt."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tā faſka tas KUNGS: Ne peewitteet juhsas Dwehseles/ ka juhs faſkat: Tee Kaldeēri tee-fchaim no mumis aisees nobst/ io tee ne afsees."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo jepſchu juhs fantat wiffu to Kaldeēro Spehku/ kas prett jums karro / un atlisktu (tikkai) no teem kahdi eewainott Wihri / tad zeltees tee ikkatrs sawā Zelti/ un fadedsinahs scho Pilssfahtu ar Ugguni."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehl tas notikke/ kad to Kaldeēru Spehks no Jerusale-mes bij aigahjis/ Warauſs Kar-ra-Spehka dehs."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad isqahje Jeremijus no Jerusalemes/ ka wiꞥſch us Ben-jamina Semmi staigatu/ un at-schkr-"
